# vhs script — clean CLI screenshot. Wider terminal so output doesn't wrap.
Output docs/cli.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1300
Set Height 440
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8

Hide
Type "cd /Volumes/Projects/mincut-context"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "mcx pack 'min-cut budget-constrained selection' --budget 1500 --exclude tests/** dist/** node_modules/**"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
